  "detailed_description": "WARNING: If you are playing this game for the first time, please be aware that you may find the game difficult and may require repeated failures.<br><br>'Hide Alone' is a first-person survival horror game where you survive for a limited time.<br>It is a story that takes place when the protagonist, who is usually interested in supernatural phenomena, becomes interested in the dangerous game of hide and seek, which can only be played at 3 am.<br>This dangerous game requires no one in the house and only you and your doll play hide and seek.<br>At 3am the doll comes to life, and you have to turn off all the lights and rely on your lighter in the dark.<br>There are rules to follow when playing hide-and-seek, and breaking even one of these rules can put your life at risk.<br>Therefore, you will need to familiarize yourself with the rules and be careful not to get caught by them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>HAUNTED DOLL</u></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/e75a3294595c9a441c519346da5b67d7.poster.avif?t=1734016310\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/e75a3294595c9a441c519346da5b67d7.webm?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/e75a3294595c9a441c519346da5b67d7.mp4?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When hide and seek begins, a haunted doll will wander around looking for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>FIND ITEM</u></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/495a5fe16eded555b133cae6edd9f748.poster.avif?t=1734016310\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/495a5fe16eded555b133cae6edd9f748.webm?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/495a5fe16eded555b133cae6edd9f748.mp4?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You will have to find the items you need to survive in the dark.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>CURSING GIRL</u></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/112c3020934a46ea67f4db7053190c1d.poster.avif?t=1734016310\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/112c3020934a46ea67f4db7053190c1d.webm?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/112c3020934a46ea67f4db7053190c1d.mp4?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The girl who curses you will keep following you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>FOLLOW THE RULES</u></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/d6c104201237c0be1b53e53409a569fe.poster.avif?t=1734016310\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/d6c104201237c0be1b53e53409a569fe.webm?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/d6c104201237c0be1b53e53409a569fe.mp4?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you want to finish hide and seek safely, you must follow the rules.",
  "about_the_game": "WARNING: If you are playing this game for the first time, please be aware that you may find the game difficult and may require repeated failures.<br><br>'Hide Alone' is a first-person survival horror game where you survive for a limited time.<br>It is a story that takes place when the protagonist, who is usually interested in supernatural phenomena, becomes interested in the dangerous game of hide and seek, which can only be played at 3 am.<br>This dangerous game requires no one in the house and only you and your doll play hide and seek.<br>At 3am the doll comes to life, and you have to turn off all the lights and rely on your lighter in the dark.<br>There are rules to follow when playing hide-and-seek, and breaking even one of these rules can put your life at risk.<br>Therefore, you will need to familiarize yourself with the rules and be careful not to get caught by them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>HAUNTED DOLL</u></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/e75a3294595c9a441c519346da5b67d7.poster.avif?t=1734016310\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/e75a3294595c9a441c519346da5b67d7.webm?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/e75a3294595c9a441c519346da5b67d7.mp4?t=1734016310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When hide and seek begins, a haunted doll will wander around looking for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>FIND ITEM</u></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2024300/extras/495a5fe16eded555b133cae6edd9f748.poster.avif?t=1734016310\" width=608 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c